インタフェースの使用
org.bukkit.scoreboard.Scoreboard

  • Scoreboardを使用しているパッケージ 
    パッケージ 説明
    org.bukkit.entity
    Interfaces for non-voxel objects that can exist in a world, including all players, monsters, projectiles, etc.
    org.bukkit.scoreboard
    Interfaces used to manage the client side score display system.

    • org.bukkit.entityでのScoreboardの使用

      Scoreboardを返すorg.bukkit.entityのメソッド 
      修飾子とタイプ メソッドと説明
      Scoreboard Player.getScoreboard()
      Gets the Scoreboard displayed to this player
      Scoreboard型のパラメータを持つorg.bukkit.entityのメソッド 
      修飾子とタイプ メソッドと説明
      void Player.setScoreboard(Scoreboard scoreboard)
      Sets the player's visible Scoreboard.

    • org.bukkit.scoreboardでのScoreboardの使用

      Scoreboardを返すorg.bukkit.scoreboardのメソッド 
      修飾子とタイプ メソッドと説明
      Scoreboard ScoreboardManager.getMainScoreboard()
      Gets the primary Scoreboard controlled by the server.
      Scoreboard ScoreboardManager.getNewScoreboard()
      Gets a new Scoreboard to be tracked by the server.
      Scoreboard Team.getScoreboard()
      Gets the Scoreboard to which this team is attached
      Scoreboard Score.getScoreboard()
      Gets the scoreboard for the associated objective.
      Scoreboard Objective.getScoreboard()
      Gets the scoreboard to which this objective is attached.
